                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310512-178-off1042 t18310512-178-crimeloc1044"></join>; the prisoner came and took off my cap, and ran away with it - I saw him in custody the same day, not long afterwards.</p>
               <p>CAROLINE HURST. I live at No. 8, Elizabeth-court, Whitecross-street. On the 4th of May I was at the bottom of the court, and saw the prisoner run up the court; I saw 
               <persName id="t18310512-178-person1335">
                  Ann 
                  Gazeley
