             pick up a cap behind a door in Mrs. Powell's passage - the prisoner ran in that direction.</p>
               <p>ANN GAZELEY. I live in Elizabeth-court. I saw the prisoner come up the court - I found this cap in Mrs. Powell's passage, which is about thirty yards from Old-street.</p>
